    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Molding your unique chakra, you mold a pair of flaming wings of your description on your back. While this jutsu is active, you gain a flying speed equal to your movement speed, your movement does not incur attacks of opportunity. Additionally, you can use an action to do the following;</p><p><em><strong>Bird Bomb</strong></em>: If you are below 60ft in the air, you hastily fly upward before diving down at breakneck speeds. Choose an area within 60ft of you; all creatures within 10ft of the area must make a Dexterity Saving throw or take 3d8 fire damage and 3d8 bludgeoning damag. Using Blazing Wings this manner ends this jutsu immediately after resolving its effects.-</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. Increase your flying speed by 15ft, and for every rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank. When you use Bird Bomb, increase its damage by an additional 1d8 fire and bludgeoning damage for every rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank.</p>",
